OL,5,Casylum
OL,7,FHowever, Cooper has already admitted
OL,8,Fthat human rights laws could be an
OL,9,Fobstacle in deporting foreign sex
OL,10,Foffenders but told ITV News "we will
OL,11,Fbe robust in our response to" any
OL,12,Fchallenges to removals.
OL,14,FThe government's amendment will also
OL,15,Fwork to tackle the asylum backlog. It
OL,16,Fhas set a 24-week target for first-
OL,17,Ftier immigration tribunals to decide
OL,18,Fon appeals of those living in asylum
OL,19,Fseeker supported accommodation, or who
OL,20,Fare foreign national offenders.
