OL,3,CHow the Home Office plans to stop
OL,4,Cforeign sex offenders claiming UK
OL,5,Casylum
OL,7,FPreviously, the threshold was a
OL,8,Fcustodial sentence of two years or
OL,9,Fmore but in 2022 that threshold was
OL,10,Flowered to 12 months.
OL,12,FThe government is now seeking to
OL,13,Fchange the law again so that anyone
OL,14,Fconvicted of a crime which places them
OL,15,Fon the Sex Offenders Register -
OL,16,Fregardless of the length of a
OL,17,Fcustodial sentence - will be denied
OL,18,Frefugee status.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/22
