OL,8,FEnver Solomon said: "The Refugee
OL,9,FConvention rightly allows governments
OL,10,Fto exclude those who commit serious
OL,11,Fcrimes from its protections. All
OL,12,Fcrimes should be considered on a case
OL,13,Fby case basis, including those placed
OL,14,Fon the sex offenders register, to
OL,15,Fensure that public safety is a
OL,16,Fpriority."
