OL,4,Cforeign sex offenders claiming UK
OL,5,Casylum
OL,7,FCooper said the Home Office wants to
OL,8,Ftackle cases like the Clapham chemical
OL,9,Fattacker Abdul Ezedi, who was granted
OL,10,Fasylum despite being a convicted sex
OL,11,Foffender.
OL,13,FEzedi killed himself within hours
OL,14,Fafter he was suspected of dousing his
OL,15,Fex-girlfriend with alkali when he
OL,16,Fattacked her and her children in south
OL,17,FLondon in January last year.
OL,19,FThe 35-year-old was convicted in 2018
OL,20,Fafter pleading guilty to sexual
OL,21,Fassault and exposure.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/22
