OL,7,FEzedi later challenged the Home
OL,8,FOffice's two refusals and in 2020 was
OL,9,Fgranted asylum by a judge who accepted
OL,10,Fhe was a Christian convert and that he
OL,11,Fwould be in danger because of his
OL,12,Ffaith if he returned to his home
OL,13,Fcountry of Afghanistan.
