OL,4,Cforeign sex offenders claiming UK
OL,5,Casylum
OL,7,FThe government is reviewing the use of
OL,8,FArticle 8 of the European Convention
OL,9,Fon Human Rights (ECHR) - the right to
OL,10,Fprivate and family life - in
OL,11,Fimmigration cases in the UK.
OL,13,FIt is particularly focusing on cases
OL,14,Fwhere ministers have disagreed with
OL,15,Fconclusions reached in the courts,
OL,16,Fafter several deportation attempts
OL,17,Fhave been halted by how the ECHR
OL,18,Fclause has been interpreted in UK law.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/22
