OL,7,FShadow Home Secretary Chris Philp
OL,8,Fargued the measures are "too little,
OL,9,Ftoo late from a Labour Government that
OL,10,Fhas scrapped our deterrent" of the
OL,11,FRwanda policy.
OL,13,F"Foreign criminals pose a danger to
OL,14,FBritish citizens and must be removed,
OL,15,Fbut so often this is frustrated by
OL,16,Fspurious legal claims based on human
OL,17,Frights claims, not asylum claims," he
OL,18,Fadded.
