OL,7,F"The Conservatives had already tabled
OL,8,Ftough, clear reforms to remove all
OL,9,Fforeign criminals and to disapply the
OL,10,FHuman Rights Act so activists and
OL,11,Flawyers cannot block deportations. But
OL,12,FLabour voted against our measures -
OL,13,Fthey are not serious about controlling
OL,14,Four borders."
