OL,7,FThe amendment will also set a 24-week
OL,8,Ftarget for first-tier immigration
OL,9,Ftribunals to decide on appeals of
OL,10,Fthose living in asylum seeker
OL,11,Fsupported accommodation, or who are
OL,12,Fforeign national offenders, in a bid
OL,13,Fto cut the asylum backlog.
OL,15,FThe Home Office also announced that
OL,16,Fartificial intelligence will be used
OL,17,Fto support caseworkers processing
OL,18,Fasylum claims, such as by summarising
OL,19,Finterview transcripts and accessing
OL,20,Fcountry advice.
