OL,7,FSome 9,885 people had been logged as
OL,8,Fmaking the journey from France as of
OL,9,FSunday, according to provisional Home
OL,10,FOffice figures.
OL,12,FIf the figure is reached it would be
OL,13,Fthe earliest point in a calendar year
OL,14,Fsince data on crossings was first
